  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `./erigon --version`\r\nChecked on latest version of alpha branch\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Windows/Linux/OSX\r\n\r\nCommit hash : 68e35417fc \r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nAncient blocks in snapshots are pruned if --snap.keepblock is false (default behavior) and aborts if it is set\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nThis appears to do the the opposite:\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  969) func (br *BlockRetire) PruneAncientBlocks(tx kv.RwTx) error {\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  970) \tif !br.snapshots.cfg.KeepBlocks {\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  971) \t\treturn nil\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  972) \t}\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  973) \tcurrentProgress, err := stages.GetStageProgress(tx, stages.Senders)\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  974) \tif err != nil {\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  975) \t\treturn err\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  976) \t}\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  977) \tcanDeleteTo := CanDeleteTo(currentProgress, br.snapshots)\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  978) \tif _, _, err := rawdb.DeleteAncientBlocks(tx, canDeleteTo, 100); err != nil {\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  979) \t\treturn nil\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  980) \t}\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  981) \tif err := rawdb.PruneTable(tx, kv.Senders, canDeleteTo, context.Background(), 100); err != nil {\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  982) \t\treturn err\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  983) \t}\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  984) \treturn nil\r\n68e35417fc (Alex Sharov                 2022-07-23 11:09:16 +0700  985) }\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\nLaunch erigon with old enough blocks in the snapshot database\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\n````\r\n[backtrace]\r\n````\r\n",
